  "title": "Accounts & Admin Executive #82058",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Management of Companies and Enterprises</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Accounts & Admin Executive</strong></li><li>Working Location: Tuas (Company transportation provided)</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days (Monday – Friday, 8:30 AM – 4:30 PM)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary + Meal Allowance + AWS</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent Role</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Manage daily bookkeeping and bank reconciliations.</li><li>Handle accounts payable (AP) and accounts receivable (AR).</li><li>Prepare and process invoices, payments, and expense claims.</li><li>Support monthly, quarterly, and yearly financial closing activities.</li><li>Assist with GST submissions and tax filings, where applicable.</li><li>Prepare financial reports and support audit activities.</li><li>Provide general office administrative support, including filing, scheduling, and correspondence.</li><li>Manage office supplies and maintain an organised workplace.</li><li>Liaise with vendors on property investment and maintenance matters.</li><li>Perform other ad-hoc duties as assigned.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma/Degree in Accounting, Business Administration, or a related field.</li><li>At least 2 years of relevant accounting and administrative experience.</li><li>Detail-oriented, organised, and able to multitask.</li><li>Able to work independently and handle confidential information with care.</li><li>Responsible, able to meet deadlines, and able to comply with data privacy requirements.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#82058 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Angel Lim | EA Reg No.: R1769781</p>",
